review_text: I have been trying a few different supplements for sleep support, and these gummies were one of them. Gaia products are always high quality with clean ingredients which I appreciate. I definitely feel sleepy and relaxed about 30 minutes after eating 3 gummies, and have been sleeping better since focusing on my night routine.

Not sure yet if it helps to sleep sound but let’s give it a try, first results are rather positive. Size should have one instead of two gummies per serving. Dosage should be reworked. Packaging is a bit to much as once empty it’s a putty to throw that glass jar.

Ate two pills before bed an hour ago, sleeping quality enhanced. Tried for a week and will keep using before working days. The smell is not so good and i take it with water just like taking pills. Its packaging is solid and easy to open. Delivery on time tho.
Great “stuff,” albeit not cheap great flavor and I find it to be much better than a standard 3mg of melatonin. I’d rush out to buy more if/when on sale.

I bought it because I thought it was trustworthy and reliable after searching for a company that produces products with good ingredients and quality based on reviews. It's in gummy form, so it's easy to take and the ingredients are good. The size is just right and it's easy to take, so I'm going to try one or two at a time, and I hope it works.

It's a nutritional supplement in the form of a gummy jelly that doesn't taste sweet, but I took two an hour before going to bed. I don't know the specific effects, but the size is just right, and the ingredients listed aren't bad, so I didn't have any resistance to taking them.

The taste is herbal. The size is not large, a jelly candy. The ingredient is a wonderful combination of soothing, natural, organic herbs. The advantage is that they act quickly, in the form of jelly candies, organic, like all the products of this company, which I really like. It was especially nice to take it this time in time for the promotion, they are available rarely and in small quantities, so I advise you to take at least 2 jars to last at least a month.

This gummy tastes like a mix of dried prunes and oranges, and has a slightly grainy texture. If you continue using it for about a month, the effects will gradually appear, but each bottle contains 40 tablets, so if you take two tablets at a time, it will be gone in 20 days. In my case, I didn't notice any effects after about a week.
If you can't fall asleep just by eating it, you need to take it with sleeping pills. However, the dosage of sleeping pills can be reduced. It tastes good and has some benefits.
